DESCRIPTION:

Strava Connect is an intelligent sports activity analysis platform that integrates
with the Strava API to provide actionable insights about your athletic performance
based on weather conditions, temperature ranges, wind impact, and optimal training
conditions.

FEATURES:
- OAuth 2.0 integration with Strava
- Intelligent weather-based performance analysis
- Multi-backend architecture (Java Spring + FastAPI + Streamlit)
- Free-tier API integration (OpenWeather, Strava)
- Docker containerization for easy deployment
- Comprehensive documentation and testing

SUPPORTED PLATFORMS:
- Linux
- macOS
- Windows

MINIMUM REQUIREMENTS:
- Java 21 (Spring Backend)
- Python 3.11+ (FastAPI, Streamlit)
- Docker 20.10+ (Optional, for containerized deployment)

DEVELOPMENT STARTED: November 2025

---

For more information, visit:
https://github.com/getavares/strava-connect-java

